name: CP-08 Isolated Power Supply
details:
10-outlet isolated power supplyThis Isolated Power supply is our original design. To produce perfect tone and supply stable current, we use high quality loops of wire. Short-circuit protection design make the pedals more safe. The housing material is aluminium alloy, as a result, the host is very stable and 
light(the host only 1.5kg). It's freely for player to carry it everywhere. Hoping this model would bring more fun in your life.
Isolated outlets total:
6x9v 100mA
2X9V 300mA
1X12V 300mA
1X18V 300mA
